<?php

namespace App\DTO;

use Spatie\LaravelData\Attributes\MapInputName;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Attributes\MapOutputName;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Attributes\Validation\Nullable;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Data as SpatieLaravelDataObj;

class TestDTO extends SpatieLaravelDataObj
{
	/**
	 * @param string|null $string
	 * @param int|null $int
	 * @param float|null $float
	 * @param string[]|null $stringArray
	 * @param int[]|null $intArray
	 * @param mixed|null $emptyArray
	 * @param \App\DTO\NestedArray|null $nestedArray
	 */
	public function __construct(
		public ?string $string = null,
		public ?int $int = null,
		public ?float $float = null,
		#[MapInputName('string_array'), MapOutputName('string_array')] public ?array $stringArray = null,
		#[MapInputName('int_array'), MapOutputName('int_array')] public ?array $intArray = null,
		#[MapInputName('empty_array'), MapOutputName('empty_array'), Nullable] public mixed $emptyArray = null,
		#[MapInputName('nested_array'), MapOutputName('nested_array')] public ?NestedArray $nestedArray = null,
	) {
	}
}
